Project Details
What is the name of your project?
Motivator

How many hours did you spend developing this?
4.5 hours

What problem does your extension solve, or what makes it unique?
This extension helps students stay motivated by displaying a daily inspirational quote, tracking tasks, and visualizing progress in a simple, easy-to-access pop-up widget. What makes it unique is its combination of motivation and task management in a straightforward interface.

How many people have tested your extension?
5 people (My friends)

Does your extension work in both Chrome and Firefox?
Yes, I believe so

Additional Comments
I built this out of interest, because I struggle with motivation.

